{"tid":2307681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「估地方」穿越時空 崖上的波妞即將上影","createTime":"2020-12-01T10:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T11:06:49.000Z","uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"84c67d12fd0dc9702c151259b5c2b2be5a1bf0f7","tid":2307681,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F3gMJuh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF3gMJuh.png&h=5a5ffaf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n微博睇到個陣以為穿越時空<br />\n定出崖上的波妞2 我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《崖上的波妞》是由宮崎駿導演、編劇，吉卜力工作室製作的長篇動畫電影，於2008年7月19日在日本首映。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哈爾移動城堡班支那人都重未有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7867e5c8d93932198c20bcbee995c2f59ae687a","tid":2307681,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5063dc25e709a372e8042923350fa66c82b3ae91","tid":2307681,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:24:38.000Z","msg":"又想幫大陸宣傳電影 屌你老父"},{"pid":"ac37b1359ed01a60f9c62de0eeeb26e03cf089f1","tid":2307681,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"風起了應該2100年 支那人會有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45565517cbc49962e151acc6a9d3a72dce03cb7b","tid":2307681,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5063dc25e709a372e8042923350fa66c82b3ae91","tid":2307681,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1